    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but putting on a patch feels like lying to the system. it's just delaying the inevitable. it feels like the more i try to fix myself, the more i just mess up the rest of the data. wouldn't it be cleaner if the sector just... went dark? like, instead of being this constant error message, wouldn't it be better to just accept that the erasure is the right thing to do?",
